title: Euro 2008 Win 1.0 (English)
description:
UEFA Euro description
An application that allows you to view the schedule for all UEFA 2008 football playoffs
An application for managing the UEFA Euro 2008 Austria-Switzerland Championship. With this program you can view the match schedule, save the final score, show both groups and second stage table, build and export statistics and, optionally, you can also update the results on-line.With UEFA Euro everyone can be up to date with the latestes UEFA socker playoffs.
